    <string name="pp_desc_1">
        "Journeys through slopes and wilderness may prove challenging even for experienced travellers and sportspeople alike.\n\n"
        "Misadventure can arise at any moment, and changing weather conditions may scatter a known trail with hazards and change the environment to better suit disaster."
    </string>
    <string name="pp_desc_2">
        "This companion suite is designed to help plan your journeys ahead of time with an all-in-one set of weather and mapping tools to help you visualise adverse weather conditions before they strike.\n\n"
        "Use the Drawing tool to demarcate areas of elevated risk before your expedition, and the system will notify you accordingly should you stray into them."
    </string>
    <string name="pp_desc_3">
        "Our system is based on cooperation between itself and the user: your honesty in profiling determines the effectiveness and accuracy of our knowledge system, and can help us best support you while you request it.\n\n"
        "Please complete the survey resources truthfully, as the safety of yourself and your companions may depend on it."
    </string>

